<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
    
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFEB3B;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/03/21/48/06/360_F_321480639_mVJIrZLLOH0pEd00Bo2vw1LA3k8IpnjR.jpg');
            background-repeat: repeat;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #F44336;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-links ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }


        .navbar.active {
            width: 400px; 
        }

        .dropdown-details {
        position: relative;
        }

        .dropdown-details .dropdown-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        background-color: #ef5b50;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 10px;
        }

        .dropdown-details .dropdown-item {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .dropdown-details a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .dropdown-details a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #2196F3;  
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #4CAF50; 
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;  
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #388E3C;  
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #E0E0E0;  
            border: 1px solid #BDBDBD;  
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .card img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
    </style>
    <title>Lego Collection</title>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/'}) %>
   
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Embark on a Lego Journey</h1>
            <p>Dive into a universe made of bricks, dreams, and creativity.</p>
            <a href="/lego/sets" class="btn">Begin Adventure</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/10592-1.jpg" alt="Town Lego Set">
                <h2>Town Creation</h2>
                <p>The vibrant essence of town life encapsulated in Lego.</p>
                <a href="/lego/sets/10592-1" class="btn">Discover</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/10584-1.jpg" alt="Duplo Lego Set">
                <h2>Duplo Dreams</h2>
                <p>The delightful world of Duplo, molded in Lego.</p>
                <a href="/lego/sets/10584-1" class="btn">Unveil</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/10577-1.jpg" alt="Castle Lego Set">
                <h2>Castle Chronicles</h2>
                <p>Revisit the medieval times with this regal Lego masterpiece.</p>
                <a href="/lego/sets/10577-1" class="btn">Explore</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>

</html>
